    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds good in theory but sounds a bit optimistic lol. my margins are already super thin and i dont have a huge cushion for extra payroll. wont the higher costs just force people to raise prices or even lay people off? i feel like that would hurt my customers more than help them.",
